{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.1","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:1","prev_osis_id":"Acts.003.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Pierre et Jean arr\u00eat\u00e9s et traduits devant le sanh\u00e9drin<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-22: cf. Ac 3:1-16. Mt 10:17-20, 26-33. Jn 15:20, 21. 1 Pi 3:14, 15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Tandis que Pierre et Jean parlaient au peuple, survinrent les sacrificateurs, le commandant du temple, et les sadduc\u00e9ens,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.2","name":"Actes 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.3.26","name":"Actes 3:26","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.3.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.2","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:2","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>m\u00e9contents de ce qu\u2019ils enseignaient le peuple, et annon\u00e7aient en la personne de J\u00e9sus la r\u00e9surrection des morts.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.3","name":"Actes 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.1","name":"Actes 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.3","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:3","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ils mirent les mains sur eux, et ils les jet\u00e8rent en prison jusqu\u2019au lendemain; car c\u2019\u00e9tait d\u00e9j\u00e0 le soir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.4","name":"Actes 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.2","name":"Actes 4:2","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.4","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:4","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Cependant, beaucoup de ceux qui avaient entendu la parole crurent, et le nombre des hommes s\u2019\u00e9leva \u00e0 environ cinq mille.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.5","name":"Actes 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.3","name":"Actes 4:3","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.5","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:5","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Le lendemain, les chefs du peuple, les anciens et les scribes, s\u2019assembl\u00e8rent \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.6","name":"Actes 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.4","name":"Actes 4:4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.6","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:6","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>avec Anne, le souverain sacrificateur, Ca\u00efphe, Jean, Alexandre, et tous ceux qui \u00e9taient de la race des principaux sacrificateurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.7","name":"Actes 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.5","name":"Actes 4:5","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.7","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:7","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Ils firent placer au milieu d\u2019eux Pierre et Jean, et leur demand\u00e8rent: Par quel pouvoir, ou au nom de qui avez-vous fait cela?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.8","name":"Actes 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.6","name":"Actes 4:6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.8","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:8","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Alors Pierre, rempli du Saint-Esprit, leur dit: Chefs du peuple, et anciens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.9","name":"Actes 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.7","name":"Actes 4:7","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.9","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:9","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>puisque nous sommes interrog\u00e9s aujourd\u2019hui sur un bienfait accord\u00e9 \u00e0 un homme malade, afin que nous disions comment il a \u00e9t\u00e9 gu\u00e9ri,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.10","name":"Actes 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.8","name":"Actes 4:8","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.10","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:10","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>sachez-le tous, et que tout le peuple d\u2019Isra\u00ebl le sache! C\u2019est par le nom de J\u00e9sus-Christ de Nazareth, que vous avez crucifi\u00e9, et que Dieu a ressuscit\u00e9 des morts, c\u2019est par lui que cet homme se pr\u00e9sente en pleine sant\u00e9 devant vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.11","name":"Actes 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.9","name":"Actes 4:9","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.11","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:11","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>J\u00e9sus est<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    La pierre rejet\u00e9e par vous qui b\u00e2tissez,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et qui est devenue la principale de l\u2019angle.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.12","name":"Actes 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.10","name":"Actes 4:10","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.12","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:12","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Il n\u2019y a de salut en aucun autre; car il n\u2019y a sous le ciel aucun autre nom qui ait \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9 parmi les hommes, par lequel nous devions \u00eatre sauv\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.13","name":"Actes 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.11","name":"Actes 4:11","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.13","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:13","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019ils virent l\u2019assurance de Pierre et de Jean, ils furent \u00e9tonn\u00e9s, sachant que c\u2019\u00e9taient des hommes du peuple sans instruction; et ils les reconnurent pour avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 avec J\u00e9sus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.14","name":"Actes 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.12","name":"Actes 4:12","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.14","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:14","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Mais comme ils voyaient l\u00e0 pr\u00e8s d\u2019eux l\u2019homme qui avait \u00e9t\u00e9 gu\u00e9ri, ils n\u2019avaient rien \u00e0 r\u00e9pliquer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.15","name":"Actes 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.13","name":"Actes 4:13","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.15","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:15","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Ils leur ordonn\u00e8rent de sortir du sanh\u00e9drin, et ils d\u00e9lib\u00e9r\u00e8rent entre eux, disant: Que ferons-nous \u00e0 ces hommes?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.16","name":"Actes 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.14","name":"Actes 4:14","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.16","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:16","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Car il est manifeste pour tous les habitants de J\u00e9rusalem qu\u2019un miracle signal\u00e9 a \u00e9t\u00e9 accompli par eux, et nous ne pouvons pas le nier.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.17","name":"Actes 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.15","name":"Actes 4:15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.17","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:17","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Mais, afin que la chose ne se r\u00e9pande pas davantage parmi le peuple, d\u00e9fendons-leur avec menaces de parler d\u00e9sormais \u00e0 qui que ce soit en ce nom-l\u00e0.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.18","name":"Actes 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.16","name":"Actes 4:16","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.18","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:18","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et les ayant appel\u00e9s, ils leur d\u00e9fendirent absolument de parler et d\u2019enseigner au nom de J\u00e9sus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.19","name":"Actes 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.17","name":"Actes 4:17","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.19","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:19","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Pierre et Jean leur r\u00e9pondirent: Jugez s\u2019il est juste, devant Dieu, de vous ob\u00e9ir plut\u00f4t qu\u2019\u00e0 Dieu;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.20","name":"Actes 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.18","name":"Actes 4:18","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.20","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:20","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>car nous ne pouvons pas ne pas parler de ce que nous avons vu et entendu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.21","name":"Actes 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.19","name":"Actes 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.21","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:21","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Ils leur firent de nouvelles menaces, et les rel\u00e2ch\u00e8rent, ne sachant comment les punir, \u00e0 cause du peuple, parce que tous glorifiaient Dieu de ce qui \u00e9tait arriv\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.22","name":"Actes 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.20","name":"Actes 4:20","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.22","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:22","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Car l\u2019homme qui avait \u00e9t\u00e9 l\u2019objet de cette gu\u00e9rison miraculeuse \u00e9tait \u00e2g\u00e9 de plus de quarante ans.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.23","name":"Actes 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.21","name":"Actes 4:21","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.23","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:23","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.024,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 23-31: cf. Ps 2:1-4. (2 R 19:14-19. Mt 18:19, 20.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 rel\u00e2ch\u00e9s, ils all\u00e8rent vers les leurs, et racont\u00e8rent tout ce que les principaux sacrificateurs et les anciens leur avaient dit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.24","name":"Actes 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.22","name":"Actes 4:22","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.24","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:24","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019ils l\u2019eurent entendu, ils \u00e9lev\u00e8rent \u00e0 Dieu la voix tous ensemble, et dirent: Seigneur, toi qui as fait le ciel, la terre, la mer, et tout ce qui s\u2019y trouve,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.25","name":"Actes 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.23","name":"Actes 4:23","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.25","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:25","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>c\u2019est toi qui as dit par le Saint-Esprit, par la bouche de notre p\u00e8re, ton serviteur David:<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">\n    Pourquoi ce tumulte parmi les nations,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et ces vaines pens\u00e9es parmi les peuples?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.26","name":"Actes 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.24","name":"Actes 4:24","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.26","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:26","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Les rois de la terre se sont soulev\u00e9s,<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Et les princes se sont ligu\u00e9s<\/p>\n<p class=\"q\">Contre le Seigneur et contre son Oint.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.27","name":"Actes 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.25","name":"Actes 4:25","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.27","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:27","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>En effet, contre ton saint serviteur J\u00e9sus, que tu as oint, H\u00e9rode et Ponce Pilate se sont ligu\u00e9s dans cette ville avec les nations et avec les peuples d\u2019Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.28","name":"Actes 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.26","name":"Actes 4:26","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.28","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:28","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>pour faire tout ce que ta main et ton conseil avaient arr\u00eat\u00e9 d\u2019avance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.29","name":"Actes 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.27","name":"Actes 4:27","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.29","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:29","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Et maintenant, Seigneur, vois leurs menaces, et donne \u00e0 tes serviteurs d\u2019annoncer ta parole avec une pleine assurance,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.30","name":"Actes 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.28","name":"Actes 4:28","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.30","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:30","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>en \u00e9tendant ta main, pour qu\u2019il se fasse des gu\u00e9risons, des miracles et des prodiges, par le nom de ton saint serviteur J\u00e9sus.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.31","name":"Actes 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.29","name":"Actes 4:29","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.31","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:31","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"q\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Quand ils eurent pri\u00e9, le lieu o\u00f9 ils \u00e9taient assembl\u00e9s trembla; ils furent tous remplis du Saint-Esprit, et ils annon\u00e7aient la parole de Dieu avec assurance.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.32","name":"Actes 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.30","name":"Actes 4:30","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.32","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:32","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.033,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Union et charit\u00e9 des croyants<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 32-37: cf. Ac 2:44-47. 1 Jn 3:16-19. Lu 12:33. 2 Co 8:13-15; 9:9.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>La multitude de ceux qui avaient cru n\u2019\u00e9tait qu\u2019un c\u0153ur et qu\u2019une \u00e2me. Nul ne disait que ses biens lui appartinssent en propre, mais tout \u00e9tait commun entre eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.33","name":"Actes 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.31","name":"Actes 4:31","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.33","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:33","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>Les ap\u00f4tres rendaient avec beaucoup de force t\u00e9moignage de la r\u00e9surrection du Seigneur J\u00e9sus. Et une grande gr\u00e2ce reposait sur eux tous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.34","name":"Actes 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.32","name":"Actes 4:32","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.34","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:34","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Car il n\u2019y avait parmi eux aucun indigent: tous ceux qui poss\u00e9daient des champs ou des maisons les vendaient, apportaient le prix de ce qu\u2019ils avaient vendu,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.35","name":"Actes 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.33","name":"Actes 4:33","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.35","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:35","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>et le d\u00e9posaient aux pieds des ap\u00f4tres; et l\u2019on faisait des distributions \u00e0 chacun selon qu\u2019il en avait besoin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.36","name":"Actes 4:36","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.34","name":"Actes 4:34","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.36","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:36","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.004.037,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Joseph, surnomm\u00e9 par les ap\u00f4tres Barnabas, ce qui signifie fils d\u2019exhortation, L\u00e9vite, originaire de Chypre,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.37","name":"Actes 4:37","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.35","name":"Actes 4:35","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.37","label":"","reference":"Actes 4:37","prev_osis_id":"Acts.004.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.005.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.4.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>vendit un champ qu\u2019il poss\u00e9dait, apporta l\u2019argent, et le d\u00e9posa aux pieds des ap\u00f4tres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.4","name":"Actes 4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.5.1","name":"Actes 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.5.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.4.36","name":"Actes 4:36","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.4.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fba8deb40.63857681');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fba8deb40.63857681\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fba8deb40.63857681","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fba8deb40.63857681'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fba8deb40.63857681\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}